âœ… Initialize philosopherâ€™s attributes:

id

meals_eaten

last_meal_time

left_fork and right_fork

Reference to t_data structure.
âœ… Set dead flag to 0 (not dead).

4. Threads and Actions

âœ… Create one thread per philosopher.
âœ… Handle one-philosopher case: He should die after picking up a fork.
