âœ… Handle memory allocation failures.
âœ… Check for deadlocks: Ensure correct mutex locking/unlocking.
âœ… Ensure no out-of-bounds memory access.

6. Debugging & Performance

âœ… Valgrind: No memory leaks (valgrind --leak-check=full ./philo).
